<div class="comment" id="comment3575">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20081202133813/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/134/" target="_top">こう。</a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20081202133813/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/3575/">#3575</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/10/30 01:30 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/10/30 01:30 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20081202133813/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/c/">
